    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name>Vuistrifuso</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Aricauso</name></persName> germani, avitatoribus in
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/165" key="#Churches">Sexto</placeName>, filii
                            <persName>quondam <name>Autelmi</name></persName>, donano pro anima
                        ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3321"
                            key="#Churches #Private_foundations">Sancti Miniati</orgName> sita in
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/165" key="#Churches">Sexto</placeName>,
                        pertinentes <rs key="#Domus #Mother_churches">domui episcoporum</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Domus #Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName> istius <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Domus #Mother_churches" ref="#places/4">Lucensis
                            civitatis</placeName>, qui est <rs key="#Churches #Private_foundations"
                            >fundata ipsa ecclesia <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3321"
                                key="#Churches #Private_foundations">Sancti Miniati</orgName> a
                            parentibus nostris</rs>; in primis ibidem <rs key="#Salae">sala
                            nostra</rs> illa ante ipsa ecclesia <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3321" key="#Churches #Private_foundations"
                            >Sancti Miniati</orgName>, qui est da partibus trasmontane cum
                        fundamento et edeficio suo: et est <rs key="#Confinia">tenente uno
                            caput</rs> in <rs key="#Curtes">curte nostra</rs>, quas nobis
                        reservamus, alio caput tene in ipsa ecclesia, cum curticella et pergula de
                        partibus aquilonis, cum aliquantula terra post ipsa sala da partibus
                        meridie, qui lato tene in <rs
                            key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention">vinea domni
                            regis</rs>, hec omnia in integrum; simul cum subdita illa, qui est
                        avembrata ad suprascripta ecclesia cum terra […] da partibus aquilone,
                        quomodo signa posita sunt; quidem et orto illo post ipsa [ecclesia] da
                        exurgente, cum aulives et arboribus suis in integrum: lato uno tene in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention"
                            >terra domni regis</rs> et alio lato tene <rs>in via, quas a comune
                            reservamus</rs>, caput uno in <rs>oliveto</rs>, quas nobis reservamus,
                        quomodo signa posite sunt. Similiter offerimus in ipsa ecclesia
                            <rs>vinea</rs> nostra illa ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/3334"
                            key="#Confinia #Rivers #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Roads #Emperor/king"
                            >ad Ponte</placeName>, qui uno caput et uno lato tene in <rs
                            key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alio caput in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention"
                            >terra domni regis</rs>, et alio lato tene in <rs key="#Rivers">rivo
                            Fisona</rs>, per designatas locas in integrum; quidem et casa nostra
                        illa in suprascripto loco ubi dicitur <placeName>ad Panicale</placeName>;
                        casa ipsa cum fundamento et edeficio suo curte, orto, seo vinea et oliveto,
                        totum insimul tenente ambo capita in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention"
                            >terra domni regis</rs>, lato uno tene in via, alio lato tene in
                        suprascripto <rs key="#Rivers">rivo Fisona</rs>; (…) una cum <rs>molino</rs>
                        illo quas infra ipse designate locas in suprascripto <rs key="#Rivers">rivo
                            Fisona</rs> esse videtur, cum <rs key="#Infrastructures">omne edeficio
                            et conciatura</rs> sua in integrum. (…) Pena in duplum. <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name>Teufridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive la cartula. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Domus #Mother_churches">Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: </ab>
                </div>
